flowchart TD
    A[User opens channel/DM] --> B{Unread messages?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Show WYMS bar]
    B -->|No| D[No WYMS bar]
    C --> E{User clicks expand?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Generate summary]
    E -->|No| G[Stay compact]
    F --> H[Show expanded summary]
    H --> I{User dismisses?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Mark as read]
    I -->|No| H
    G --> K{User dismisses?}
    K -->|Yes| J
    K -->|No| G
    J --> L[Hide WYMS bar]
